name: Etnor
description: [Beast | Fighter] 'Son of Eross' Active: Pay 100 Gold during your MP1 and Discard One Card from your Hand to the Graveyard; Add Eross from your deck to your hand. Passive: If Etnor is sent to the grave, Hire Eross to the field from your hand.
